Package com.notkamui.javaisyou.engine.rule.rulepart.property

Interface Property

All Superinterfaces:
HasImage, RightOperand, RulePart
All Known Implementing Classes:
Property.Boom, Property.Defeat, Property.Hot, Property.Melt, Property.Push, Property.Sink, Property.Stop, Property.Win, Property.You
public sealed interface Property
extends RightOperand
permits Property.Push, Property.Stop, Property.Melt, Property.Hot, Property.Defeat, Property.Sink, Property.You, Property.Win, Property.Boom
Represents objects that are property types A property knows its type and its images

  • Nested Class Summary

    Nested Classes
    Modifier and Type Interface Description
    static class  Property.Boom
    The BOOM property An element with BOOM will instantly disappear, along with all elements directly next to it
    static class  Property.Defeat
    The DEFEAT property An element with DEFEAT will make a superimposed YOU element disappear
    static class  Property.Hot
    The HOT property An element with HOT will make a superimposed MELT element disappear
    static class  Property.Melt
    The MELT property An element with MELT disappears when superimposed with an element with HOT
    static class  Property.Push
    The PUSH property An element with PUSH can be pushed (therefore, cannot be walked over)
    static class  Property.Sink
    The SINK property An elements with SINK will make any superimposed element disappear along with itself
    static class  Property.Stop
    The STOP property An element with STOP cannot be walked over
    static class  Property.Win
    The WIN property An element with WIN will make the state of the level as won if superimposed with a YOU element
    static class  Property.You
    The YOU property An element with YOU can be controlled by the player, will disappear if superimposed with a DEFEAT element, and will make the state of the level as won if superimposed with a WIN element
